    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-09-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-09-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="782"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d782">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-09-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 30, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister for foreign affairs gave joint entertainment yesterday to the two
                    Commissions. Passed off very agreeably. Meet for business to-morrow.
                    Commissioners will be presented, to the President of France on Tuesday. Can you
                    send word of greeting to him to be delivered at our presentation?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
